<!-- Solutions -->
<section class="section bg-cream">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header centered">
            <span class="section-eyebrow">Solutions</span>
            <h2>Mining Water Management Solutions</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="three-col-grid">
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🛣️</div>
                <h3>Haul Road Dust Suppression</h3>
                <p>Automated drip and spray systems keep unpaved haul roads within permit limits. Sensors trigger watering only when dust potential is high, minimizing water waste.</p>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>PM10/PM2.5 sensor integration</li>
                    <li>Automated weather-based controls</li>
                    <li>Tanker fill station connectivity</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🌱</div>
                <h3>Mine Reclamation &amp; Revegetation</h3>
                <p>Establish vegetation on reclaimed mine land using drip irrigation systems designed for slopes, poor soils, and harsh conditions. Increase revegetation success rates dramatically.</p>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>Slope-compatible dripline installation</li>
                    <li>Erosion blanket integration</li>
                    <li>Native seed germination programs</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🏔️</div>
                <h3>Tailings Dam Vegetation</h3>
                <p>Establish plant cover on tailings impoundments to reduce wind erosion, improve visual screening, and satisfy closure plan requirements.</p>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>Subsurface and surface drip options</li>
                    <li>Chemigation for pH adjustment</li>
                    <li>Works with saline or high-salt water</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">⚗️</div>
                <h3>Process Water Reuse</h3>
                <p>Treat and reuse mine process water for irrigation and dust control, reducing freshwater withdrawals and discharge permit compliance challenges.</p>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>High-solids tolerant emitters</li>
                    <li>Disc and screen filtration packages</li>
                    <li>Flush manifold systems</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">💨</div>
                <h3>Crusher &amp; Transfer Point Dust</h3>
                <p>Misting bars and fog cannons at crushers, conveyor transfer points, and stockpiles reduce fugitive dust at the source — without saturating material.</p>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>Fog nozzle systems</li>
                    <li>Automated on/off with conveyor belts</li>
                    <li>Wind speed cutoff sensors</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🔧</div>
                <h3>Site Engineering &amp; Installation</h3>
                <p>Our mining irrigation engineers provide complete hydraulic design, equipment selection, and on-site installation support for new mines and expansions.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn-outline-dark mt-md">Request Engineering Consultation</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

